td.div: Español: Bandera de Venezuela 1930-2006, cuando es usada por el estado venezolano.
English: State Flag of Venezuela 1930-2006, New flag was introduced 13 March 2006.

tr.td:
yellow, blu, red
flag has 3 horizontal stripes
A horizontal tricolor of yellow, blue and red with the National Coat of Arms on the upper hoist-side of the yellow band and an arc of seven white five-pointed stars centered on the blue band.
See File history below for details.
